In the coming days you will be hearing from many of the 400,000 licensed saltwater anglers from not only here in NC, but from around the country! Please listen to them! When NOAA recently released its study on the 23 coastal states, one of the Co-authors of that study, Scott Steinback, actually did the calculations for us for accuracy. The entire study can be viewed at this link.. <http://www.st.nmfs.noaa.gov/st5/publication/marine_angler.html>http://www.st.nmfs.noaa.gov/st5/publication/marine_angler.html



