   My name is Michael Daniels, I am a registered democrat in Beaufort County and I supported you with my vote in this past Novembers election. I am also an ex-commercial fisherman and an avid recreational fisherman.

   The reason for my email is I would like your support with H-918 (Game Fish Status for Speckled Trout and Red Drum), in my many travels throughout the Gulf of Mexico region I have seen firsthand what game fish status can do for the economy of a coastal state, I have also seen how many of the commercial fishermen in these states have became charter captains or guides and are now making a better living than they did as commercial fisherman.

